" }}{PARA 257 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 172 "Factor each polynomial and determi
ne whether Maple was able to find enough linear factors to demonstrate
 the above assertion about the appropriate number of linear factors." 
}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 
